{
  "stem": "17845.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 767.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because the Joint was sending clothes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't have much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So, I used to help them to go to collect and to-- it wasn't new clothing-- but everybody-- so I felt important, put it this way.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, well for-- for the-- I don't know how many.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was maybe a couple of thousand people there living, mostly young.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Later, my parents arrived from Cracow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they-- they allocated also a-- a room in one of the barracks, was also for the parents.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they were staying with us for a while.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I met my husband there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Somebody introduced us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And somehow it clicked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was going out, I had some other boyfriends.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But somehow when I met him, I decided that may be the one.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we illegally decided to go over to-- to-- to-- to Italy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My parents, they still stayed back in-- in the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we went, the two of us illegally to-- through the mountains, walking the whole night, until we arrived to the Italian border, on some date.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the Italian [? gendarmerie ?] was bribed, the police.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that helped a lot, really, to go over the border.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everything was illegal.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they knew about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, you couldn't really go through the border and people not know about it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But somehow it was hush-hushed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were going from Austria to Italy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Again to a kibbutz, again to a kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when we arrived to Italy we went-- one of the very known and very rich Italian Jews gave away his holiday villa for our kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Commander [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he gave us away his summer villa.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And where we actually married there, it was a little village out of Milano, 30 kilometer by train, called Albiate [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
